<span style="color: #339966;"><span style="font-size: large;">Wendy&#8217;s Restaurants: </span></span> &#8220;Loyal  Emails are tailored for us to get the message out to existing customers  month to month all kinds of new customers regarding special events.</span></span></p>
<p>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><br />
<span style="color: #339966;"><span style="font-size: large;">Bay Center Recreation Bowling:</span></span> &#8220;We canceled Val Pack because customers use our coupons more from Loyal  Email. Our rep keeps everything simple for us. Very cost effective.&#8221;</span></span></p>
<p>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<br />
